e for drivers throughout the country. Alternatively, visit Kia Bradford and Scarborough, Lexus in Birmingham, Wolverhampton and Leeds, ŠKODA in Morecambe for a great deal on quality new or used vehicles. Our Citroën dealerships are located in Morecambe and Blackpool; with a Hyundai dealership covering Preston, whilst Honda looks after the Barnsley, Bradford and Leeds areas. For more information about our full range of new and used cars or to find out about our after sales services, Motability vehicles or business solutions, just click on our contact page which gives a full listing of all our dealerships. We will be delighted to meet you and are here to help with whatever you need. Make sure you 'like' us at Vantage Motor Group on Facebook or follow us @VantageMotorGrp on Twitter for all the latest Vantage news, product updates and exciting competitions!                  Find out more about Vantage Motor Group   Take a look                             Twitter  Glowing praise for the team at #Lexus #Leeds from Wendy.
